<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.6.7">
<l>maṇṇāṭum viṇṇāṭum vāṉavarun tāṉavarum maṟṟumellām</l>
<l>uṇṇāta peruveḷḷa muṇṇāmal tāṉviḻuṅki yuyyakkoṇṭa</l>
<l>kaṇṇāḷaṉ kaṇṇamaṅkai nakarāḷaṉ kaḻalcūṭi yavaṉaiyuḷḷat</l>
<l>teṇṇāta māṉiṭattai yeṇṇāta pōtellā miṉiyavāṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>All of the time that [we] do not reflect on the people</l>
<l rend="indent">who do not reflect on him in their hearts,</l>
<l>Crowning [themselves] with [his] ankleted [feet],</l>
<l rend="indent">the ruler of the city of Kaṇṇamaṅkai, [our] companion</l>
<l>Who took the earth realm, the sky realm, deities and demons,</l>
<l rend="indent">and everything else to save [them],</l>
<l>Gulping them so that the great unconsumable flood</l>
<l rend="indent">would not consume [them], how sweet!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
